+====================================================================================================+
|                                      QMD MASTER ARCHITECTURE                                       |
+====================================================================================================+
| External interfaces                                                                                |
|                                                                                                    |
|  +--------------------+       +--------------------+       +--------------------+                  |
|  | terminal           |       | TypeScript callers |       | MCP clients        |                  |
|  | argv/stdout/stderr |       | import qmd SDK     |       | stdio or HTTP      |                  |
|  +---------+----------+       +---------+----------+       +---------+----------+                  |
|            |                            |                            |                             |
|            v                            v                            v                             |
|  +--------------------+       +--------------------+       +--------------------+                  |
|  | CLI                |       | SDK                |       | MCP server         |                  |
|  | src/cli/qmd.ts     |       | src/index.ts       |       | src/mcp/server.ts  |                  |
|  | commands/formats   |       | QMDStore facade    |       | tools/resources    |                  |
|  +---------+----------+       +---------+----------+       +---------+----------+                  |
|            |                            |                            |                             |
|            +----------------------------+----------------------------+                             |
|                                         |                                                          |
|                                         v                                                          |
|  +================================================================================================+ |
|  | Core store: src/store.ts                                                                       | |
|  |                                                                                                | |
|  |  +--------------------+       +--------------------+       +--------------------+              | |
|  |  | retrieval          |       | indexing           |       | maintenance        |              | |
|  |  | find/get/multi_get |       | reindexCollection  |       | cache/orphan/vacuum|              | |
|  |  +---------+----------+       +---------+----------+       +---------+----------+              | |
|  |            |                            |                            |                         | |
|  |            v                            v                            v                         | |
|  |  +--------------------+       +--------------------+       +--------------------+              | |
|  |  | FTS/BM25           |       | content-addressing |       | query cache        |              | |
|  |  | searchFTS          |       | hashContent        |       | llm_cache          |              | |
|  |  +---------+----------+       +---------+----------+       +---------+----------+              | |
|  |            |                            |                            |                         | |
|  |            v                            v                            v                         | |
|  |  +--------------------+       +--------------------+       +--------------------+              | |
|  |  | hybrid fusion      | <---- | chunking           | ----> | vector search      |              | |
|  |  | RRF + rerank blend |       | regex + AST        |       | searchVec          |              | |
|  |  +---------+----------+       +---------+----------+       +---------+----------+              | |
|  +============|============================|============================|==========================+ |
|               |                            |                            |                            |
|               v                            v                            v                            |
|  +------------------------+     +------------------------+     +------------------------+           |
|  | SQLite DB              |     | Markdown filesystem    |     | LLM layer              |           |
|  | documents              | <---| collection roots       |     | src/llm.ts             |           |
|  | content                |     | **/*.md files          |     | node-llama-cpp         |           |
|  | documents_fts          |     +------------------------+     +-----------+------------+           |
|  | store_collections      |                                           |                        |
|  | store_config           |                                           v                        |
|  | content_vectors        |                                +------------------------+           |
|  | vectors_vec            | <------------------------------| GGUF model cache       |           |
|  | llm_cache              |       embeddings/rerank cache  | ~/.cache/qmd/models    |           |
|  +-----------+------------+                                +------------------------+           |
|              ^                                                                                   |
|              |                                                                                   |
|  +-----------+------------+       +------------------------+       +------------------------+      |
|  | DB compatibility       |       | Collections/config     |       | AST sidecar            |      |
|  | src/db.ts              |       | src/collections.ts     |       | src/ast.ts             |      |
|  | Bun: bun:sqlite        |       | YAML source of truth   |       | web-tree-sitter        |      |
|  | Node: better-sqlite3   |       | inline SDK config      |       | code breakpoints       |      |
|  | sqlite-vec loading     |       +-----------+------------+       +-----------+------------+      |
|  +------------------------+                   |                                ^                  |
|                                               v                                |                  |
|                                    +------------------------+                  |                  |
|                                    | YAML config stores     |                  |                  |
|                                    | ~/.config/qmd/*.yml    |                  |                  |
|                                    | .qmd/index.yaml        | -----------------+                  |
|                                    +------------------------+   chunkStrategy=auto                 |
|                                                                                                    |
+====================================================================================================+
| Search query flow                                                                                  |
|                                                                                                    |
|  CLI/SDK/MCP query                                                                                 |
|      > Store hybridQuery/structuredSearch                                                          |
|      > searchFTS(original + lex)                                                                   |
|      > LLM expandQuery if BM25 not strong                                                          |
|      > LLM embedBatch(original + vec + hyde)                                                       |
|      > SQLite vectors_vec cosine search                                                            |
|      > reciprocalRankFusion                                                                        |
|      > chunk selected candidates with regex/AST                                                    |
|      > LLM rerank selected chunks unless disabled                                                  |
|      > snippets/context/docids                                                                     |
|      > stdout, SDK result, MCP content/resource                                                     |
|                                                                                                    |
| Indexing job flow                                                                                  |
|                                                                                                    |
|  CLI/SDK update                                                                                    |
|      > load YAML or inline config                                                                  |
|      > syncConfigToDb(store_collections/store_config)                                              |
|      > fast-glob markdown files                                                                    |
|      > read UTF-8 body from filesystem                                                             |
|      > SHA-256 hash and title extraction                                                           |
|      > insert/update documents + content                                                           |
|      > rebuild documents_fts with CJK normalization                                                |
|      > deactivate missing docs                                                                     |
|      > cleanup orphaned content                                                                    |
|      > CLI/SDK embed                                                                               |
|      > chunkDocumentByTokens                                                                       |
|      > LLM formatDocForEmbedding + embedBatch                                                      |
|      > content_vectors + vectors_vec                                                               |
+====================================================================================================+
